    "Management": {
      "text": "Emergent ophtho consultation\nTopical antibiotics\nVigamox 1 drop qhour\nOR\nCiprofloxacin\n2gtt q15 min x6 hours, then q30min x18h, then q1h x1 day, then q4h x12d\nConsider\nantiviral\nor\nantifungal\nif high suspicion for viral or fungal cause (rare)\nCycloplegic\nmay help if iritis present\nCyclopentolate\n1%\nDo not patch the eye\nTdap update is not strictly required\nConsider gentle irrigation and if there is suspicion for contamination",
      "subsections": {},
      "tables": [],
